{
  "book": "enos",
  "bookName": "Enos",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": "bm_george",
  "duration": 562.675,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.9,
      "end": 4.475,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Enos's Childhood and Father's Teachings",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 5.375,
      "end": 9.025,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then behold, I, Enos, knowing my father",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 9.205,
      "end": 11.53,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he was a just man\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 11.71,
      "end": 14.51,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he taught me in his language,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 14.69,
      "end": 18.965,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also in the nurture and admonition of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 19.145,
      "end": 22.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and blessed be the name of my God for it\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 22.925,
      "end": 27.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will tell you of the wrestle which I had before God,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 27.43,
      "end": 31.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before I received a remission of my sins.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 32.96,
      "end": 35.76,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Hunting and Spiritual Wrestle",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 36.66,
      "end": 40.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I went to hunt beasts in the forests;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 40.315,
      "end": 44.265,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the words which I had often heard my father speak",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 44.445,
      "end": 47.12,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning eternal life",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 47.3,
      "end": 51.075,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the joy of the saints, sunk deep into my heart.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 52.655,
      "end": 55.855,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Mighty Prayer and Wrestle with God",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 56.755,
      "end": 58.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my soul hungered;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 59.06,
      "end": 62.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I kneeled down before my Maker,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 62.315,
      "end": 64.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cried to him",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 64.57,
      "end": 68.82,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in mighty prayer and supplication for my own soul;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 69.0,
      "end": 72.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all the day long did I cry to him;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 72.555,
      "end": 74.955,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and when the night came",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 75.135,
      "end": 78.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I did still raise my voice high",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 78.315,
      "end": 80.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it reached the heavens.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 82.245,
      "end": 85.345,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Divine Forgiveness and Assurance",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 86.245,
      "end": 88.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there came a voice to me, saying:",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 89.1,
      "end": 92.275,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Enos, your sins are forgiven you,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 92.455,
      "end": 94.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you shall be blessed.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 95.385,
      "end": 98.91,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew that God could not lie;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 99.09,
      "end": 101.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, my guilt was swept away.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 102.47,
      "end": 105.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said: Lord, how is it done?",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 107.1,
      "end": 110.625,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Lord Promises Lamanite Salvation",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 111.525,
      "end": 113.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 113.58,
      "end": 116.43,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Because of your faith in Christ,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 116.61,
      "end": 119.885,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whom you have never before heard nor seen.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 120.065,
      "end": 122.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many years pass away",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 122.97,
      "end": 126.645,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before he shall manifest himself in the flesh;",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 126.825,
      "end": 128.375,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, go,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 128.555,
      "end": 131.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "your faith has made you whole.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 132.86,
      "end": 135.91,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Praying for the Nephites and Lamanites",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 136.81,
      "end": 139.385,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now, when I had heard these words",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 139.565,
      "end": 144.44,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I began to feel a desire for the welfare of my brothers, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 144.62,
      "end": 148.12,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I poured out my whole soul to God for them.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 148.8,
      "end": 152.0,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And while I was thus struggling in the spirit,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 152.18,
      "end": 156.78,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the voice of the Lord came into my mind again, saying:",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 156.96,
      "end": 159.585,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will visit your brothers",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 159.765,
      "end": 163.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to their diligence in keeping my commandments.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 164.12,
      "end": 166.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have given to them this land,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 167.15,
      "end": 169.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it is a holy land;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 169.955,
      "end": 172.03,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I curse it not",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 172.21,
      "end": 175.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "except for the cause of iniquity;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 175.44,
      "end": 179.565,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I will visit your brothers according as I have said;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 179.745,
      "end": 184.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their transgressions will I bring down with sorrow upon their own heads.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 185.675,
      "end": 189.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I, Enos, had heard these words,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 189.505,
      "end": 193.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my faith began to be unshaken in the Lord;",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 193.36,
      "end": 198.735,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I prayed to him with many long strugglings for my brothers, the Lamanites.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 200.315,
      "end": 203.69,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Divine Covenant Regarding Records",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 204.59,
      "end": 208.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I had prayed and labored with all diligence,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 209.12,
      "end": 211.295,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord said to me:",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 211.475,
      "end": 215.225,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will grant to you according to your desires,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 215.405,
      "end": 217.63,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of your faith.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 219.21,
      "end": 222.46,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Enos Requests Eternal Record",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 223.36,
      "end": 227.96,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold, this was the desire which I desired of him\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 228.14,
      "end": 230.415,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if it should so be",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 230.595,
      "end": 233.245,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my people, the Nephites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 233.425,
      "end": 236.125,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should fall into transgression,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 236.305,
      "end": 239.13,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by any means be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 239.31,
      "end": 242.385,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lamanites should not be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 242.565,
      "end": 247.49,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God would preserve a record of my people, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 247.67,
      "end": 251.695,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even if it so be by the power of his holy arm,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 251.875,
      "end": 256.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it might be brought forth at some future day to the Lamanites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 256.43,
      "end": 260.005,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that, perhaps, they might be brought to salvation\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 260.685,
      "end": 264.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For at the present our strugglings were vain",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 264.315,
      "end": 267.49,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in restoring them to the true faith.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 267.67,
      "end": 270.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they swore in their wrath that,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 270.7,
      "end": 272.675,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it were possible,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 272.855,
      "end": 276.155,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would destroy our records and us,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 276.335,
      "end": 279.985,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also all the traditions of our fathers.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 280.665,
      "end": 282.54,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, I knowing",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 282.72,
      "end": 286.945,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God was able to preserve our records,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 287.125,
      "end": 291.05,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I cried to him continually, for he had said to me:",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 291.23,
      "end": 294.655,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Whatsoever thing you shall ask in faith,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 294.835,
      "end": 298.86,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "believing that you shall receive in the name of Christ,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 299.04,
      "end": 301.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you shall receive it.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 302.62,
      "end": 305.645,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Seed of Fathers Also Had Faith",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 306.545,
      "end": 308.345,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I had faith,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 308.525,
      "end": 310.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cried to God",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 310.88,
      "end": 313.68,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would preserve the records;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 313.86,
      "end": 316.41,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he covenanted with me",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 316.59,
      "end": 321.215,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would bring them forth to the Lamanites in his own due time.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 321.895,
      "end": 326.87,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew it would be according to the covenant which he had made;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 327.05,
      "end": 329.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so my soul rested.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 330.105,
      "end": 332.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord said to me:",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 332.485,
      "end": 336.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Your fathers have also required of me this thing;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 336.44,
      "end": 340.365,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it shall be done to them according to their faith;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 340.545,
      "end": 343.27,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for their faith was like to your.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 344.85,
      "end": 348.05,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Enos's Ministry and Testimony",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 348.95,
      "end": 353.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Enos, went about among the people of Nephi,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 353.43,
      "end": 356.23,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prophesying of things to come,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 356.41,
      "end": 360.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and testifying of the things which I had heard and seen.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 361.44,
      "end": 365.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I bear record that the people of Nephi sought diligently",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 366.07,
      "end": 370.145,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to restore the Lamanites to the true faith in God.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 370.325,
      "end": 372.8,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But our labors were vain;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 372.98,
      "end": 375.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their hatred was fixed,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 375.485,
      "end": 378.685,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were led by their evil nature",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 378.865,
      "end": 383.665,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they became wild, and ferocious, and a blood-thirsty people,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 383.845,
      "end": 386.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "full of idolatry and filthiness;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 387.15,
      "end": 390.925,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feeding upon beasts of prey; dwelling in tents,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 391.105,
      "end": 394.305,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and wandering about in the wilderness",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 394.485,
      "end": 399.11,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with a short skin belt about their waist and their heads shaven;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 399.29,
      "end": 403.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their skill was in the bow, and in the cimeter, and the ax.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 403.895,
      "end": 408.12,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many of them ate nothing save it was raw meat;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 408.3,
      "end": 411.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were continually seeking to destroy us.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 412.455,
      "end": 415.83,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the people of Nephi tilled the land,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 416.01,
      "end": 419.51,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and raise all manner of grain, and of fruit,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 419.69,
      "end": 421.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of herds,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 422.07,
      "end": 426.12,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of all manner of cattle of every kind,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 426.3,
      "end": 430.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and goats, and wild goats, and also many horses.",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 431.08,
      "end": 434.205,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there were very many prophets among us.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 434.385,
      "end": 438.66,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the people were a stiffnecked people, hard to understand.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 440.24,
      "end": 443.74,
      "type": "pericope",
      "text": "Enos's Old Age and Final Witness",
      "verse": "",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 444.64,
      "end": 448.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there was nothing save it was great harshness,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 448.345,
      "end": 453.42,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "preaching and prophesying of wars, and contentions, and destructions,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 453.6,
      "end": 456.875,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and continually reminding them of death,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 457.055,
      "end": 460.03,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the duration of eternity,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 460.21,
      "end": 463.36,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the judgments and the power of God,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 463.54,
      "end": 467.29,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all these things\u2014stirring them up continually",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 467.47,
      "end": 470.87,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to keep them in the fear of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 471.05,
      "end": 474.425,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I say there was nothing short of these things,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 474.605,
      "end": 477.555,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and very great plainness of speech,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 477.735,
      "end": 481.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "would keep them from going down speedily to destruction.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 482.115,
      "end": 485.94,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner do I write concerning them.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 486.62,
      "end": 491.92,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw wars between the Nephites and Lamanites in the course of my days.",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 492.6,
      "end": 495.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I began to be old,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 495.53,
      "end": 499.93,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and an hundred and seventy and nine years had passed away",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 500.11,
      "end": 504.135,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that our father Lehi left Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 504.815,
      "end": 508.615,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw that I must soon go down to my grave,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 508.795,
      "end": 512.37,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having been wrought upon by the power of God",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 512.55,
      "end": 516.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I must preach and prophesy to this people,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 516.43,
      "end": 521.03,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and declare the word according to the truth which is in Christ.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 521.21,
      "end": 524.41,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I have declared it in all my days,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 524.59,
      "end": 528.14,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have rejoiced in it above that of the world.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 528.82,
      "end": 532.045,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I soon go to the place of my rest,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 532.225,
      "end": 534.9,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is with my Redeemer;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 535.08,
      "end": 538.355,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that in him I shall rest.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 538.535,
      "end": 541.26,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I rejoice in the day",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 541.44,
      "end": 545.04,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when my mortal shall put on immortality,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 545.22,
      "end": 547.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall stand before him;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 547.85,
      "end": 550.925,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then shall I see his face with pleasure,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 551.105,
      "end": 553.255,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will say to me:",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 553.435,
      "end": 555.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Come to me, you blessed,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 555.79,
      "end": 560.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there is a place prepared for you in the mansions of my Father.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 560.57,
      "end": 561.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 150
    }
  ]
}